titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 1, 5-naphthalene diisocyanate.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/2/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1995, the suspension of duty on 1,5-naphthalene diisocyanate.
